ConfigurationXmlParserSettings

class ConfigurationXmlParserSettings
extends Object

java.lang.Object
   ↳ com.android.tradefed.config.ConfigurationXmlParserSettings

A simple class to accept settings for the ConfigurationXmlParser

To pass settings to this class, the alias is mandatory. So something like --template:map name filename.xml will work, but this would NOT work: --map name filename.xml.
